    {
      "id": "methods-body",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 104,
      "y": 108,
      "width": 392,
      "height": 262,
      "text": "① Direct Slicer.exe\n   Slicer.exe --no-splash --python-script <path>\n   启动 20–40s · GUI 短暂闪烁 · 最可靠\n\n② PythonSlicer.exe (Headless)\n   PythonSlicer.exe <path>\n   启动 5–15s · 无 GUI · 批量处理首选\n\n③ Jupyter Kernel (Fallback)\n   jupyter_client KernelManager\n   需 SlicerJupyter 扩展 · 备选方案",
